Add a marketing website to this project. The marketing site is for RodeoPro, a mobile-first performance tracking app for competitive barrel racers. The site should use the same design language as the app (dark charcoal backgrounds, amber/gold #F59E0B primary, teal #0D9488 accent, white text) and serve as the public-facing landing page that converts visitors into subscribers before routing them into the app.

---

BRAND

App name: RodeoPro (styled as "RODEO" in white + "PRO" in amber gold)
Tagline: "Track Every Run. Own Every Record."
Sub-tagline: "The performance platform built for barrel racing competitors."
Brand colors:
  - Background: #111827 (primary dark), #1F2937 (card/section dark)
  - Primary accent: #F59E0B (amber gold)
  - Secondary accent: #0D9488 (teal)
  - Text: #FFFFFF primary, #9CA3AF secondary gray
  - Success: #10B981 green
  - Border/divider: #374151

---

PAGES & SECTIONS

Build a single-page marketing site with smooth scroll navigation. All sections live on one page (index/marketing route). A sticky top nav links to each section. The page ends with a footer.

---

NAV BAR (sticky, top, full width)

Left: "RODEO" (white, bold) + "PRO" (amber, bold) wordmark
Center links: Features · How It Works · Pricing
Right: "Sign In" text link (ghost) + "Start Free Trial" button (amber background, dark text, rounded)
Background: #111827 with a subtle bottom border #374151, slight blur/backdrop on scroll

---

SECTION 1 — HERO

Full-width, centered layout. Large bold headline, supporting copy, two CTAs, and a mobile phone mockup showing the app's Runs screen (dark UI, amber accents, run cards with times like "13.842s", "14.101s", horse names "Whiskey" and "Rio").

Headline: "Track Every Run.\nOwn Every Record."
Sub-copy: "RodeoPro gives barrel racers a professional-grade platform to log runs, analyze performance, and track earnings — all from your phone."
CTA 1: "Start Free Trial" — amber filled button, large, links to /app
CTA 2: "See How It Works" — ghost/outline button, scrolls to #how-it-works section
Badge below CTAs: "No credit card required · Cancel anytime"
Background: dark gradient from #111827 top to #1F2937 bottom, subtle radial amber glow behind mockup

