SECTION 5 — PRICING (id="pricing")

Section title: "Simple, Transparent Pricing"
Section sub: "One plan. Everything included. No hidden fees."

Monthly / Annual toggle switch at top center. When Annual is selected, show a green badge "Save 33%" next to the toggle. Default to Monthly.

Two pricing cards side by side, centered:

Card 1 — MONTHLY
Price: $9.99 / month
Subtext: "Billed monthly, cancel anytime."

Card 2 — ANNUAL (highlighted with amber border and "Best Value" badge)
Price: $6.99 / month
Subtext: "Billed as $83.88 / year."
When monthly toggle is active, show $9.99 on Card 1 and $6.99 on Card 2.
When annual toggle is active, show $9.99/mo on Card 1 and $6.99/mo on Card 2 (same prices, just surface the billing note).

Both cards include the same feature list with amber checkmarks:
✓ Unlimited run logging
✓ Unlimited horses & arenas
✓ Performance analytics & charts
✓ Photo & video attachments
✓ Earnings tracking
✓ Personal record tracking
✓ Clean run streaks
✓ Dark & light mode

CTA button on each card: "Start Free Trial" — Monthly card uses teal button, Annual card uses amber button (primary).

Below cards: small gray text — "Payments processed securely by Stripe. Your subscription can be cancelled at any time from your account settings."

Stripe integration notes (wire into the component):
- On "Start Free Trial" click, call Stripe Checkout with the appropriate Price ID
- Monthly Price ID: stripe_price_monthly (placeholder, to be replaced)
- Annual Price ID: stripe_price_annual (placeholder, to be replaced)
- Success redirect: /app?subscribed=true
- Cancel redirect: /#pricing
- Include a Stripe publishable key constant: VITE_STRIPE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY (read from env)
- Use @stripe/stripe-js loadStripe() to initialize
- Wrap in a <StripeCheckoutButton> component that accepts priceId and label props
- Show a loading spinner on the button while the Stripe redirect is initializing

