ROUTING

This marketing page lives at the root route "/". The existing app lives at "/app". The sticky nav "Sign In" link goes to /app. All "Start Free Trial" / "Enter RodeoPro" CTAs go to /app (or trigger Stripe checkout if a plan is being selected). Use React Router for routing between "/" and "/app".

---

TECH NOTES

- Match the existing stack: React 18, TypeScript, Vite, Tailwind CSS 4, React Router
- Reuse existing design tokens and Tailwind config from the app
- Use Lucide React for all icons (already installed)
- Install @stripe/stripe-js for Stripe Checkout integration
- All sections should be responsive: desktop (3-col grids), tablet (2-col), mobile (1-col stack)
- Animate sections into view on scroll with subtle fade-up transitions (use Framer Motion, already installed)
- The page should match the dark-mode-first aesthetic of the app exactly
